      "content": "<div class=\"article-content\">\n    <div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6\">\n        <span class=\"tag-ta px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">技术美术</span>\n        <span class=\"text-gray-500\">Sun, 29 Se</span>\n        <span class=\"text-gray-500\">•</span>\n        <span class=\"text-gray-500\">5分钟阅读</span>\n        <span class=\"text-gray-500\">•</span>\n        <span class=\"text-gray-500\">初级到中级 3D 艺术家</span>\n    </div>\n    <h1>Gnomon Workshop ZBrush 2024 入门教程发布</h1>\n    <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-300 mb-6\">Gnomon Workshop 发布了由 Madeleine Scott-Spencer 主讲的 ZBrush 2024 入门教程。这是一套广受欢迎的数字化雕刻软件教程，涵盖 ZBrush 2024 的最新功能和工作流程，适合初学者系统学习数字雕刻技术。</p>\n    <div class=\"source-box\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\">\n            <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-neon-amber\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1\"></path>\n            </svg>\n            <span class=\"text-neon-amber font-medium\">原文链接</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\">\n            <div>• <button href=\"https://www.cgchannel.com/2024/09/the-gnomon-workshop-releases-introduction-to-zbrush-2024/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-neon-blue hover:underline\">CG Channel - 查看完整原文</button></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tech-analysis-box\" style=\"border-color: #b026ff40;\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\">\n            <svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" style=\"color: #b026ff\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z\"></path>\n            </svg>\n            <span class=\"text-lg font-semibold\" style=\"color: #b026ff\">🔬 深度技术分析</span>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"mb-0 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">ZBrush 一直是数字雕刻领域的行业标准工具，2024版本带来了多项重要更新。本教程由业界资深专家 Madeleine Scott-Spencer 主讲，她在游戏和影视行业拥有丰富的雕刻经验。教程不仅涵盖基础操作，还深入讲解了 ZBrush 2024 的新特性，如改进的 DynaMesh、升级的 ZRemesher 以及全新的笔触系统。对于想要进入 3D 角色艺术领域的学习者，这套教程提供了从界面认知到复杂生物雕刻的完整学习路径。技术要点包括：理解 ZBrush 独特的 2.5D 工作流程、掌握 SubTool 管理系统、学习使用 Insert Mesh 笔刷进行硬表面建模、以及运用 Polypaint 进行顶点着色。</p>\n    </div>\n    <h2>🎯 核心技术点</h2>\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\">\n        <div class=\"bg-dark-700/50 rounded-xl p-4 border-l-4\" style=\"border-color: #b026ff\"><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold mb-1\" style=\"color: #b026ff\">ZBrush 2024 新功能</div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mb-0\">核心技术要素</p></div><div class=\"bg-dark-700/50 rounded-xl p-4 border-l-4\" style=\"border-color: #b026ff\"><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold mb-1\" style=\"color: #b026ff\">数字雕刻 workflow</div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mb-0\">核心技术要素</p></div><div class=\"bg-dark-700/50 rounded-xl p-4 border-l-4\" style=\"border-color: #b026ff\"><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold mb-1\" style=\"color: #b026ff\">硬表面建模</div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mb-0\">核心技术要素</p></div><div class=\"bg-dark-700/50 rounded-xl p-4 border-l-4\" style=\"border-color: #b026ff\"><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold mb-1\" style=\"color: #b026ff\">有机体雕刻</div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mb-0\">核心技术要素</p></div><div class=\"bg-dark-700/50 rounded-xl p-4 border-l-4\" style=\"border-color: #b026ff\"><div class=\"text-sm font-semibold mb-1\" style=\"color: #b026ff\">Polypaint 纹理绘制</div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mb-0\">核心技术要素</p></div>\n    </div>\n    <h2>💡 实用价值与应用场景</h2>\n    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-dark-700/50 to-dark-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6\">\n        <p class=\"text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-0\">为零基础学习者提供了系统学习 ZBrush 的优质资源，也适合有经验的设计师快速掌握 2024 版本的新功能</p>\n    </div>\n    <h2>🏷️ 技术标签</h2>\n    <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6\"><span class=\"tag-ta px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">ZBrush 2024 新功能</span><span class=\"tag-ta px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">数字雕刻 workflow</span><span class=\"tag-ta px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">硬表面建模</span><span class=\"tag-ta px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">有机体雕刻</span><span class=\"tag-ta px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">Polypaint 纹理绘制</span></div>\n    <h2>📚 相关技术主题</h2>\n    <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm bg-gray-700 text-gray-300\">数字雕刻</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm bg-gray-700 text-gray-300\">角色建模</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm bg-gray-700 text-gray-300\">游戏美术</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm bg-gray-700 text-gray-300\">影视资产制作</span></div>\n    <h2>👥 适合人群与难度</h2>\n    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-6\">\n        <li><strong>目标读者:</strong> 初级到中级 3D 艺术家</li>\n        <li><strong>实现难度:</strong> 中等</li>\n        <li><strong>技术领域:</strong> 技术美术</li>\n    </ul>\n    <div class=\"bg-dark-700/50 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8 border-l-4\" style=\"border-color: #b026ff\">\n        <p class=\"mb-0 text-gray-400\">\n            <strong style=\"color: #b026ff\">💡 提示:</strong> \n            本文为高质量中文技术分析，由AI基于原文深度整理。如需查看完整原文，请点击上方链接。\n        </p>\n    </div>\n</div>",
